channel.description:
[IMG]http://i1034.photobucket.com/albums/a428/kie478/Project_Biohazard.jpg[/img]
Welcome, I am restarting my development of my server but now I'm using PI because Delta fails...
One of my goals for this server is to have a reason for every skill. Ex. Fishing is useful because of Rocktails, soon I will be adding extremes so that herblore has a use.
So lets get to pictures... [IMG]http://i1034.photobucket.com/albums/a428/kie478/client.jpg[/img]
[b][size=14pt]All items have correct stats and anims :D[/size][/b] [IMG]http://i1034.photobucket.com/albums/a428/kie478/workingshit.jpg[/img]
[size=14pt][b]Adding curses so far only some done (I'm not using Tp and pretending to add curses myself ;)[/b][/size] [IMG]http://i1034.photobucket.com/albums/a428/kie478/curses.jpg[/img]
[size=14pt][B]Was bored :P[/B][/size] [IMG]http://i1034.photobucket.com/albums/a428/kie478/chatbox.jpg[/img]
[size=14pt][b]Full use of Rocktails[/b][/size] [URL=http://s1034.photobucket.com/albums/a428/kie478/?action=view&current=rocktails.mp4][IMG]http://i1034.photobucket.com/albums/a428/kie478/th_rocktails.jpg[/img][/URL]
